Players will have a clue listed.

They will click on a letter to guess the letters in the word.
When they click on the alphabet, the letter guessed it will become grayed out.

If they get a right letter it will appear in the word.
If they are wrong there will be an 'x' generated in the text screen.
If they get 6 wrong guesses the game is over.

If you win a text message will appear in the text box
If you lose a text message will appear in a the text box

Add a play again button
